  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to explore the main factors associated with the return to work of
      patients presenting an upper aero-digestive tract cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Socio-professional, medical, psychological, demographic, economic, and educational data
      collection in patients within the care pathway of upper aero-digestive tract cancer.

      A series of questionnaires will be presented at the initial consultation and then at 6
      months, at 12 months and at 18 months during follow-up visits. Medical data will be collected
      via the CRF.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
